lockquote><br />\n支那講一套做一套已經畀人睇穿曬"},{"pid":"4344860ccbbf6831b869c3b292259b13f340dc6f","tid":340380,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9958d406d4639cd1d27b3cc1dd963ebc25774c38","tid":340380,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>關中國咩事  咩都入中國數<br />\n<br />\n美帝ON99</blockquote><br />\n全世界都制裁北泡，唯獨支那仲肯養佢<br />\n把口話唔想北韓搞核武<br />\n結果由無核武變到有州際能力既核武<br />\n<br />\n咁你話唔入支那數入邊個數？</blockquote><br />\n笑左<br />\n<br />\nD黃絲一時話北韓有州際能力好危險  <br />\n<br />\n一時又話北韓得個吹字  核武州際邊有能力整到<br />\n<br />\n真係任佢地UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家又話中國有核武州際能力拿?<br />\n<br />\n中國唔係打飛機最叻咩?   咁肯定佢有核武州際能力?</blockquote><br />\n痴線<br />\n咁都叫黃絲<br />\n你係咪平時講開左改唔到口啊支那五毛狗"},{"pid":"1a8f4fcb4d717eaa4affeab40ede6f7406a4dfcd","tid":340380,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵侵行Twitter 外交<br />\n屌，快撚d試下 Ford 航母同 rail gun 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那遼寧艦應該好樂意應戰"},{"pid":"a3246edad0eb534d952166152bf757bbe98f3a3e","tid":340380,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"支那淨係賣下過期導彈比金仔都已經賺唔少 點會出手阻佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0a993f2b89dd7644abc382d367bddd233e985b","tid":340380,"uid":41154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"侵仔冇牙紙老虎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得把口，乜都做唔到  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95d065e07d6df40f486cf93180bfc18cd0f043d","tid":340380,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:03:26.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n一睇名<br />\n原來又係出名支那五毛狗<br />\n連自己講緊乜都唔知<br />\n依